name: SUKI AND THE WHISPERER
description:
Monday. 01:49 AM.

Suki lies awake, and suddenly realizes she can hear voices... 

They seem to be coming from the bathroom...

She slowly creeps along the upstairs hallway, holding in her breath as she moves closer towards the eerie, pale, moon-lit door.

"The Shadow with One Thousand Faces shall awaken..."

Did that come from the drain? Surely not...

"In the ancient twilight city of H'Thlyu..."

Where are mom and dad? Are they hearing this too?!

"... madness devours all living things... no... escape..."

Suki yells and turns to run back to her bedroom...

But she glimpses something strange in the bathroom mirror.

What's... wrong with my face?!

What is that? Is that... an eyeball?!

This can't be real. Wake up!

"The Shadow with One Thousand Faces shall awaken...

... no... escape..."

Wake up! Wake up!
